{"id": 964, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x方太】你什么时候才觉得你妈是“亲妈”？", "description": "母亲节快到了，让我们来谈谈妈这个生物：放假前很想你，等你回家嫌你懒；说你馋又忍不住让你吃这个那个…口嫌体正直典范，你妈。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5869, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183629Unhdgl68uEKj2eYR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-27T11:17:38Z", "options": [{"id": 71173, "content": "我妈总是让我对我男朋友好一点，别揍他", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 71174, "content": "“你长这么多痘啊”“你这头发咋回事”“你这裤子有点丑”", "image": null, "praise_count": 892, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 71175, "content": "手机掉水里坏掉了，让朋友给我妈说了声这事儿，怕她打不通电话，我问我朋友“我妈回复了吗？”朋友答“回复了，问你脑子有没有进水！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 417, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570540}, {"id": 71176, "content": "吃饭的时候，笑着盯着我看，快把我看化了~", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 577000}, {"id": 71432, "content": "想吃什么，跟我说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588218}, {"id": 71177, "content": "每次回家，我妈都深情地让我脱掉袜子：“你袜子太脏了别把我地板踩脏了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 73993, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4119}, {"id": 71179, "content": "吃少了说我没用，吃多了说我饭桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 71180, "content": "-“妈，我爱你！☺️”                                                                        -“要多少，直说吧”。                                               -“?”", "image": null, "praise_count": 211, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532476}, {"id": 71181, "content": "我妈把我的照片发朋友圈：我女儿单身……", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578627}, {"id": 71182, "content": "用我小时候的丑照当手机屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 532, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199459}, {"id": 71183, "content": "我问如何练刀工。我妈说多切几次手就可以了。???", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301696}, {"id": 73487, "content": "没事的，放手去做吧，你长大了，应该有自己的主见呢…加油孩子…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593656}, {"id": 71184, "content": "把LV/Chanel借给我背", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238743}, {"id": 71440, "content": "一边念叨女大不中留，生儿育女到底有神马一丝～一边马不停蹄张罗相亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586217}, {"id": 71185, "content": "不回家的时候打电话：儿子你在外头多吃点 别饿着 回家了：儿子你咋又胖了 赶紧减肥啊 不然找不着媳妇了啊", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193523lXmONDGej25qxnLp.jpg", "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274056}, {"id": 71186, "content": "我说我分手了，我妈说早该分的，你这脾气谁受得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 88, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530347}, {"id": 71188, "content": "“你是不是喜欢男的啊，跟妈说没事的。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 384, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527683}, {"id": 71189, "content": "批准我多吃并不妨碍她嫌弃我太胖的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586217}, {"id": 71190, "content": "在她关心我的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562208}, {"id": 71446, "content": "老妈总说我懒，不爱整理房间，可是每次呢都会帮我整理好，哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277369}, {"id": 71191, "content": "看你胖的看你矮的", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582489}, {"id": 71192, "content": "比我还担心我的身材……“少吃点儿都胖了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 431002}, {"id": 71448, "content": "我在朋友圈里晒新学的瘦身食谱，闺蜜们都夸我做的瘦身餐又漂亮又好吃。只有老妈说这吃的就是草，吃得面色都不好了，怎么还会美呢？", "image": "img/option/option/201606071926113k5OTErJM9jGCW4K.JPG", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588298}, {"id": 71193, "content": "越长越像她，已经看到了老年版自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579493}, {"id": 71196, "content": "不想让我出去玩但是想要儿媳妇", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 551051}, {"id": 74012, "content": "大学时候室友妈妈每天电话关心问候的，我妈从来不打，我自己打回去她一句没事我就挂了！我直接吐血三升", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 543482}, {"id": 71197, "content": "每次要刷信用卡，老妈都拿出自己的卡刷", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568220}, {"id": 71198, "content": "拿去，你这败家仔", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482853}, {"id": 71199, "content": "咱们应该比比在家呆几天，妈咪就会嫌你烦，哈哈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585503}, {"id": 71455, "content": "一边唠叨女大不中留，生儿育女到底有神马一丝，一边马不停蹄帮我张罗相亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586217}, {"id": 71200, "content": "不着急，先玩几年再找对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586668}, {"id": 71456, "content": "每天给我做好吃的，不会嫌弃我长胖，嘘寒问暖，就是亲妈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588411}, {"id": 71201, "content": "我妈一定要和我自拍 然后发朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479787}, {"id": 71457, "content": "我是我妈脑残粉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 510320}, {"id": 71458, "content": "从来不嫌弃我长得丑，总是说我是最漂亮的哪一个，亲妈哦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588416}, {"id": 71203, "content": "发公司招聘启事我妈说“帮你转了”?", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 71204, "content": "一手摸胸一手摸墙，说：一样的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438850}, {"id": 71205, "content": "今年最开心的事就是教会老妈发红包   闲着没事老妈就会发来小红包  虽然不多  但是很暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568303}, {"id": 73253, "content": "妈：说吧！又要多少钱？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591793}, {"id": 71206, "content": "每次换季的时候，我妈求着我去逛街买衣服，我说店里太贵了，还是网购实惠，我妈说：给，这里xxxx拿去买，不够再跟我说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586698}, {"id": 71207, "content": "我:“妈妈我想养狗”妈妈:“你和狗只能留一个”", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541005}, {"id": 71208, "content": "你咋胖了啊，该减肥了。   多吃点啊，吃这么少？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302846}, {"id": 71209, "content": "我妈说，你以后找男朋友一定要找会做饭的，要不然以后吃饭怎么办……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586700}, {"id": 71210, "content": "什么时候都觉得是！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169698}, {"id": 71211, "content": "我（卖萌打滚脸）：麻麻，你看我黑了！真黑了！肿么办…\n麻麻（淡定嫌弃脸）：没事，黑点遮你一脸痘=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586704}, {"id": 71212, "content": "好奇心研究所也接广告了啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296767}, {"id": 71213, "content": "来看看，这小伙子俊吧…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584984}, {"id": 71214, "content": "使劲给饭吃的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586444}, {"id": 71726, "content": "总是转发【太！危！险！啦！】种种类似注意食品安全或者突发隐患这样的群发短消息给我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590080}]}